- **applyCustomStyles Function**: This function checks if the `<form-embed>` element and its shadow root are available. If they are, it injects a `<style>` element into the shadow root with your custom CSS.

- **Disconnecting the Observer**: After applying the styles, we disconnect the observer to improve performance.

